---
// Projects section
---

<section id="projects" class="section-spacing mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 reveal">
  <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4">
    <div>
      <h2 class="h2-divider text-3xl tracking-tight">Selected Work</h2>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-300">A few things I'm building and refining.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Main Projects</p>
  <div class="mt-3 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <!-- CWM -->
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Celebrate It With Me (CWM)</h3>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-300 ring-1 ring-white/10">SaaS</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Event SaaS for weddings & quinceañeras: public event pages, RSVP flows, guest management, menus, locations,
        design themes, and modular features.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="dot-primary"></span>Laravel API + Vue 3 front-end with Pinia, Tailwind
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="dot-secondary"></span>AWS: S3 uploads, SES email, queue-ready architecture
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="dot-tertiary"></span>Theme templates + config-driven rendering (in progress)
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Laravel</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Vue 3</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Tailwind</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">AWS</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
        <a
          class="ring-brand cursor-not-allowed rounded-2xl bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 ring-1 ring-white/5"
          aria-disabled="true"
          tabindex="-1"
        >
          Demo <span class="text-xs">In progress</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="ring-brand rounded-2xl px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-primary), var(--c-secondary))"
          href="#experience"
        >
          What I built
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- OptionEdge -->
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">OptionEdge (Personal)</h3>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs text-slate-300 ring-1 ring-white/10">Fintech tooling</span>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-300">
        Concept work for an options/stock assistant: watchlists, alerts, analytics, and data pipelines. Focused on robust
        architecture and extensibility.
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 grid gap-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-primary"></span>API-first design with clean service boundaries</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-secondary"></span>Planned integrations: market data, notifications, dashboards</li>
        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="dot-tertiary"></span>Personal project (not public yet)</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Architecture</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Notifications</span>
        <span class="rounded-full bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 text-xs ring-1 ring-white/10">Pipelines</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-6 flex gap-3">
        <a
          class="ring-brand cursor-not-allowed rounded-2xl bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 ring-1 ring-white/5"
          aria-disabled="true"
          tabindex="-1"
        >
          Notes <span class="text-xs">In progress</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="ring-brand rounded-2xl px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--c-primary), var(--c-secondary))"
          href="#contact"
        >
          Talk about it
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500">Engineering Areas</p>
  <div class="mt-3 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">Public Templates</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">High-fidelity event templates with premium effects and mobile-first UX.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-400">Example: Habana Nights theme.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">Automation & AI</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Exploring n8n automations and AI-assisted workflows for product teams.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-400">Agent-style integrations planned.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="reveal rounded-3xl card-premium p-8">
      <h3 class="text-base font-semibold">Cloud & Observability</h3>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Production-minded engineering: logs, metrics, tracing, and clean deploy pipelines.</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-400">FullStory experience across apps.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dot-primary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: var(--c-primary);
  }

  .dot-secondary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: var(--c-secondary);
  }

  .dot-tertiary {
    @apply mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full;
    background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.85);
  }
</style>
